      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "This is a film still capturing a dimly lit, atmospheric restaurant or nightclub scene bathed in warm, saturated red and amber tones. In the center foreground, a small table lamp with a vivid orange-red fringed lampshade casts a glowing, textured light over a red-clothed table cluttered with liquor bottles, drinking glasses, a crystal decanter, and scattered small objects. Seated around the table are several men in suits: on the left, a man with a mustache in a dark suit smiles toward the center, while beside him another man in a gray suit with a mustache also grins, his face illuminated by the lamp's warm glow. On the right side of the frame, a man in a light cream-colored suit is shown in profile, holding a cigarette to his lips, with another man in a dark suit partially visible behind him. A standing figure in a dark suit looms in the mid-background, and the deeper background dissolves into shadowy reds with hints of additional patrons and warm ambient light sources, creating a layered, cinematic composition with low-key lighting that emphasizes the intimate, moody atmosphere of the gathering."
      ],
